column12:
'desc': [u'

Nuby Comb and Brush with Nylon Bristles Price: Rs.220

Combing your baby’s soft curls to make them grow healthy and beautiful is very important. Use the Nuby Comb and Brush Nylon Bristles
column13:
designed exclusively for the baby’s soft head.

This Nuby Brush and Comb Set ensures safe hygiene for your baby and features Soft Nylon Bristles. The Bristles gently caress your baby’s hair and help you get rid of all the knots. The Comb is gentle to the baby’s scalp so that they do not get hurt. The brush is made to be smooth and delicately combs your baby’s adorable tails. This Nuby Comb and Brush Set is simple and easy to use and can be used for both boys and girls since the time of their birth.
